{"tid":1544839,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【為咗反修例 我辭咗職】","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T20:20:58.000Z","uid":35215,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e8553fa4115ec3d2514a281a7229761b17ab66ac","tid":1544839,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"首先放咗辭職圖先，個解釋放#2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q58BJQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ58BJQa.jpg&h=991d42a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有建制派直指很多示威者已「收貨」，阿叔個fb page希望做一個大型民調了解「收貨」情況，並且了解一下事件時間線對「撤例」的看法，希望大家可以以此為理據，拒絕「被代言」。<br />\n<br />\n我們一共收集6779份問卷，當中一共<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">6564份</span></strong>為有效問卷。每題結果如下：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 98%支持反修例人士對林鄭於昨日（9月4日）最新動議撤回修例的方案不滿意，只有2%表示滿意。</strong><br />\n<strong>2. 64.2%支持反修例人士認為若果林鄭在二百萬人大遊行（6月16日）後就提出動議撤回的話會感到滿意。</strong><br />\n<strong>3. 只有5%支持反修例人士認為若果在元朗白衣人無差別襲擊事件（7月21日）後提出動議撤回的話會感到滿意。</strong><br />\n<br />\n根據上述數據，林鄭的現行方案在六月仍有機會平息部份市民的不滿情緒，或嘗試緩和社會氣氛。但隨著警暴、濫捕、警黑勾結、疑似宵禁等箝制言論及集會自由問題出現，單純撤回修例已無法滿足市民訴求。換言之，林鄭政府反應之慢將香港推往內鬥深淵，難辭其咎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLbvOfy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLbvOfy.jpg&h=47f20dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BX8YW9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBX8YW9b.jpg&h=fca28cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4U9jnC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4U9jnC.jpg&h=e21789a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBmfZny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBmfZny.jpg&h=01faabb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c6b6e264ccaa3473e1fec3f092263901175b840","tid":1544839,"uid":35215,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"Facebook post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/397572127827433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKongPollster%2Fposts%2F397572127827433&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=101d47f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/397572127827433</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/396660611251918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKongPollster%2Fposts%2F396660611251918&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=3d3abe92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/posts/396660611251918</a><br />\n<br />\n今次民調突然好多人質疑我地係鬼，又話google form會link去Facebook，又話咩一做民調就會比狗拉等等。事實係我哋成員係由一班成黎自前一大、暴大、BU理大科大嘅連登仔，喺整場反送中運動入面，我哋一直都係同大家坐同一條船&mdash;&mdash;KongPollster嘅成員亦擔任緊某大公海谷、各大文宣谷、突發消息谷嘅Admin。睇返我哋嘅文宣，唔夠膽話高質，但已經用盡力fact check整合。<br />\n<br />\n我哋為咗搞好文宣，團隊有人因而辭職，又為咗做街訪自資買器材，目的只係想係想以真實數據向社會反映民意，對抗fake news。經過今次事情後，有成員不堪壓力，想退出。講到底，我哋都係為咗呢場運動，希望將真確資訊傳俾唔同政治光譜嘅人，打破所謂同溫層文宣，為此，我哋一直有留意唔同嘅聲音，並調整我哋嘅文宣方向。<br />\n<br />\n我明白現時太多fake news，亦有太多三毛、臥底，但亦都希望各位先起一下我哋個底，唔好誤中副車。<br />\n最後再一次感謝大家嘅支持，嚟緊我哋將會繼續我哋嘅工作。如果大家認同我哋嘅理念，請關注同分享我哋Facebook page俾身邊嘅人，多謝。"},{"pid":"04e6405490081f5698115fa61ea8c9d6d0173afd","tid":1544839,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"阿叔好波😭😭"},{"pid":"42d4a3db12f27a728eeac039e1f51ff39715f72c","tid":1544839,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"加油!"},{"pid":"cb7c7d70d5b35ea36a4fd213aee5960957f529f2","tid":1544839,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed42fb38711aaf8686fce2a17